data.description: Welcome to the Wishbone Ranch! This beautiful 70 acre ranch located in Creston boasts a seasonal pond with an adorable adjacent cabin, an incredible 3,000 sf shop with bathroom, along with a party area by the pond for those fun Creston nights! 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with lots of privacy and great producing well. Enjoy the built-in income this property produces with an AT&T cell tower with approximately 20 + years lease remaining.  Complete livestock fencing and horse arena make this property ready for animals, 4H projects or starting the farm you have always envisioned. Privacy, beauty and potential right in the heart of Creston.
